sentence: The latest tally of analyst opinions from the major brokerage houses shows that among the 30 stocks making up the Dow Jones Industrial Average, Home Depot (HD) is the #10 analyst pick.
Home Depot also comes in above the median of analyst picks among the broader S&P 500 index components, claiming the #128 spot out of 500.
Looking at the stock price movement year to date, Home Depot (HD) is showing a gain of 20.9%.
